name: Vanguard Canadian Long-Term Bond Index ETF
longDescription: The investment objective of Vanguard Canadian Long Term Bond Index ETF the ETF is to track, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Bloomberg Barclays Global Aggregate Canadian 10 plus Year Float Adjusted Bond Index the Index. To achieve investment objective the fund seeks to track, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of a broad Canadianbond index with a long-term dollar weighted average maturity. Currently, this Vanguard ETF seeks to track the Bloomberg GlobalAggregate Canadian 10+ Year Float Adjusted Bond Index (or any successor thereto).
